Package: webshot
Title: Takes screenshots of web pages, including Shiny apps
Version: 0.2.1
Authors@R: "Winston Chang <winston@rstudio.com> [aut, cre]"
Description: Takes screenshots of web pages, including Shiny applications.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.0)
Imports:
    magrittr
License: GPL-2
SystemRequirements: PhantomJS (http://phantomjs.org) for taking screenshots,
    ImageMagick (http://www.imagemagick.org) or GraphicsMagick
    (http://www.graphicsmagick.org) for manipulating images.
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
